_sText:
**awp_l337sk337beta_source**

This is my first map release, don't be too critical, ha!
No actually, this was inspired by superjer's awp_l337sk337beta from 1.6 that was unfortunately never converted.

This map is kind of similar to the original, except the position of one water-skeet is not placed to the side.
The doors can only be unlocked from the outside.
The garage doors open after 60 seconds have passed.
The trap doors can only be opened from the ladders below.

##I tried to make this as similar to the original and have neglected to create any 3d skyboxes or add any special textures, but this is the first of many touch up releases.##

Special thanks to Zalos for the skeet/awp switching triggers!!


ENJOY!
